<div role="note" class="dezambiguizare">Pagina „Rebreanu” trimite aici.<i> </i>Pentru alte sensuri vedeti <a href="/wiki/Rebreanu_(dezambiguizare)" class="mw-redirect mw-disambig" title="Rebreanu (dezambiguizare)">Rebreanu (dezambiguizare)</a>.</div>
<p><b>Liviu Rebreanu</b> (n. <time datetime="1885-11-27"><a href="#" title="27 noiembrie">27 noiembrie</a> <a href="/wiki/1885" title="1885">1885</a></time>,<sup id="cite_ref-168576fbc7d2d66cc2796345c6baf1ac_1-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-168576fbc7d2d66cc2796345c6baf1ac-1">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-37a3b43cb769034e64b0d24385c58f22_2-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-37a3b43cb769034e64b0d24385c58f22-2">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-c265f045d5402440ff8e166b98d2baa2_3-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-c265f045d5402440ff8e166b98d2baa2-3">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> <a href="#
" title="Tarlisua, Bistrita-Nasaud">Tarlisua</a>, <a href="#" title="Austro-Ungaria">Austro-Ungaria</a>&#160;– d. <time datetime="1944-09-01"><a href="#" title="1 septembrie">1 septembrie</a> <a href="/wiki/1944" title="1944">1944</a></time>, <a href="/wiki/Valea_Mare,_Arge%C8%99" title="Valea Mare, Arges">Valea Mare</a>, <a href="/wiki/Rom%C3%A2nia" title="Romania">Romania</a>) a fost un prozator si dramaturg roman, membru titular al Academiei Romane.
</p>
