<p>Imaginile sunt oferite cu sprijinul <a href="/w/index.php?title=Institutul_de_Memorie_Cultural%C4%83&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Institutul de Memorie Culturala — pagina inexistenta">Institutului de Memorie Culturala</a>.
</p>
<h2><span id="Rebreanu_.C3.AEn_cultura_popular.C4.83"></span><span class="mw-headline" id="Rebreanu_in_cultura_populara">Rebreanu in cultura populara</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Liviu_Rebreanu&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=29" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" title="Modifica sectiunea: Rebreanu in cultura populara">modificare</a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Liviu_Rebreanu&amp;action=edit&amp;section=29" title="Modifica sectiunea: Rebreanu in cultura populara">modificare sursa</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<div class="thumb tright"><div class="thumbinner" style="width:222px;"><a href="/wiki/Fi%C8%99ier:Cluj-Napoca-Parcul_Simion-Barnu%C8%9Biu-Bustul.Liviu_Rebreanu-IMG_0756.JPG" class="image"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/05/Cluj-Napoca-Parcul_Simion-Barnu%C8%9Biu-Bustul.Liviu_Rebreanu-IMG_0756.JPG/220px-Cluj-Napoca-Parcul_Simion-Barnu%C8%9Biu-Bustul.Liviu_Rebreanu-IMG_0756.JPG" decoding="async" width="220" height="124" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/05/Cluj-Napoca-Parcul_Simion-Barnu%C8%9Biu-Bustul.Liviu_Rebreanu-IMG_0756.JPG/330px-Cluj-Napoca-Parcul_Simion-Barnu%C8%9Biu-Bustul.Liviu_Rebreanu-IMG_0756.JPG 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/05/Cluj-Napoca-Parcul_Simion-Barnu%C8%9Biu-Bustul.Liviu_Rebreanu-IMG_0756.JPG/440px-Cluj-Napoca-Parcul_Simion-Barnu%C8%9Biu-Bustul.Liviu_Rebreanu-IMG_0756.JPG 2x" data-file-width="3303" data-file-height="1857" /></a>  <div class="thumbcaption"><div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/Fi%C8%99ier:Cluj-Napoca-Parcul_Simion-Barnu%C8%9Biu-Bustul.Liviu_Rebreanu-IMG_0756.JPG" class="internal" title="Extinde"></a></div>Bustul lui Liviu Rebreanu (din <a href="/wiki/Cluj-Napoca" title="Cluj-Napoca">Cluj-Napoca</a> Parcul <a href="/wiki/Simion_B%C4%83rnu%C8%9Biu" title="Simion Barnutiu">Simion Barnutiu</a></div></div></div>
<ul><li>Anual, la <a href="/wiki/Aiud" title="Aiud">Aiud</a>, se desfasoara <a href="/w/index.php?title=Zilele_Culturale_%E2%80%9ELiviu_Rebreanu%E2%80%9D&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Zilele Culturale „Liviu Rebreanu” — pagina inexistenta">Zilele Culturale „Liviu Rebreanu”</a>.</li>
<li>Tot anual, la Bistrita, are loc Festivalul National de Teatru „Liviu Rebreanu”.</li>
<li>Lunar, sectia de arta a <a href="/w/index.php?title=Biblioteca_Jude%C8%9Bean%C4%83_Mure%C8%99&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Biblioteca Judeteana Mures — pagina inexistenta">Bibliotecii Judetene Mures</a> organizeaza <a href="/w/index.php?title=Cenaclul_%E2%80%9ELiviu_Rebreanu%E2%80%9D&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Cenaclul „Liviu Rebreanu” — pagina inexistenta">Cenaclul „Liviu Rebreanu”</a>.</li></ul>
